<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-05-28T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-05-28T17:00:00-05:00" n="58" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d58">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">865.014/5–2147: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Embassy in Italy</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                            </seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-05-28T18:00:00-04:00">May 28,
                                    1947—6 p. m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>787. If Yugos decline participate provisional demarcation <gloss target="#t_FTT1">FTT</gloss> frontiers (<gloss target="#t_ur1">ur</gloss> 1241 May 21<note n="1" xml:id="d58fn1">Not
                                printed.</note>), <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss> considers
                            US, <gloss target="#t_UK1">UK</gloss> and France shd proceed with
                            delimitation all frontiers of <gloss target="#t_FTT1">FTT</gloss> in
                            territory presently under <gloss target="#t_AMG1">AMG</gloss> (<gloss target="#t_Deptel1">Deptel</gloss> 632 May 2<note n="2" xml:id="d58fn2">Department telegram 281, May 2, to Belgrade,
                                repeated to Rome as 632, not printed.</note>). You may advise <gloss target="#t_FonOff1">FonOff</gloss> informally of <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss>’s views, and express hope Itals will
                            participate regardless of Yugo decision.</p>
                        <p>(Sent Rome as 787 rptd London as 2307 Moscow as 1239 Paris as 1950 and
                            Belgrade as 348.)</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>